    Description
    AbstractServices<T,ID>
    The AbstractServices class is an abstract base class for service implementations.
    CenyService
    The CenyService class provides service methods for managing pricing information (represented by the Ceny entity) in the application.
    HoteleService
    The HoteleService class provides service methods for managing hotel entities (represented by the Hotele class) in the application.

    The KlienciService class provides service methods for managing client data (represented by the Klienci entity) within the application.

    The ListyHoteliService class provides service methods for managing hotel list entries, represented by the ListyHoteli entity, in the application.
    MiastaService
    The MiastaService class provides service operations for managing cities (represented by the Miasta entity) in the system.
    MiastaWycieczekService
    The MiastaWycieczekService class provides service methods for managing trip night city assignments, represented by the MiastaWycieczek entity.
    PokojeService
    The PokojeService class provides service methods for managing room entities (represented by the Pokoje class) in the application.
    TypyWycieczekService
    The TypyWycieczekService class provides service operations for managing trip types (represented by the TypyWycieczek entity) in the application.

    The WycieczkiService class provides service methods for managing trip entities (represented by the Wycieczki class) in the application.
